public abstract class ResourceSetPropertySourceEObjectFactory<T extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject,P extends SemanticProcessor<T>> extends PropertySourceEObjectFactory<T,P>
Uses ResourceSet to load objects from spec-uri. Text specs get encoded into a data URL by creating a JSON object with spec, format, and base fields. The object is converted to string and base64 encoded. application/json-eobject-spec is used as media type.
Author:
Pavel
